message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>As the senior Paralegal and Legal Assistant, I will ensure all exhibits are properly organized and ready for trial. This includes labeling each exhibit, creating a detailed exhibit list, and coordinating with the legal team to ensure all necessary documents are included. I will also assist in preparing witness binders and coordinating with expert witnesses to ensure they are ready to testify. Additionally, I will review all trial materials to ensure accuracy and completeness before the trial begins.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
